data.description: Hurry! 3 bed 2 full bath Brick Ranch in Fern Creek. Big back yard with a ginormous 4 car carport, an approximately 24 x 12 out building and lots of mature threes. Cozy living room features brick surround wood burning fireplace, eat-in kitchen with a patio door that leads to the deck and back yard. 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms and laundry. Heating and Colling replaced in the last 2 years. Windows replaced. Roof replaced in 2015.
